Seq2Seq - based basic models.from sentence: The performances of the Seq2Seq - based basic models including Seq2Seq , Seq2Seq + Attention , and Seq2Seq + Copying are very low .

SQLNet and TypeSQL.from sentence: In contrast , SQLNet and TypeSQL that utilize SQL structure information to guide the SQL generation process significantly outperform other Seq2Seq models .

all models.from sentence: As Component Matching results in shows , all models struggle with WHERE clause prediction the most .

over all performances.from sentence: In general , the over all performances of all models are low , indicating that our task is challenging and there is still a large room for improvement .
